reskillable.unlock.reskillable.obsidian_smasher = 黑曜石破坏者
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.obsidian_smasher.desc = 显著提高使用钻石镐破坏黑曜石的速度
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.fossil_digger = 化石开采者
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.fossil_digger.desc = 在使用不带有精准采集附魔的铁镐或更高等级的镐子挖掘煤矿时有很小的概率掉落两个煤炭
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.ore_cascade = 连锁挖矿
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.ore_cascade.desc = 切换能力：挖掘一个矿物方块时将导致整个矿脉都被挖掘下来而镐子会掉落双倍的耐久
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.lucky_fisherman = 幸运渔夫
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.lucky_fisherman.desc = 增加钓鱼时的运气
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.drop_guarantee = 掉落保障
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.drop_guarantee.desc = 如果敌对生物有掉落物，那么将必定掉落至少一个物品
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.neutralissse = 拆弹专家
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.undershirt = 内衣
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.undershirt.desc = 每过 10 秒钟，当你的生命值超过 3 颗心时，对你造成的致命的一击会将你的生命值减少到半颗心，而不是将你击杀
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.transmutation = 紫颂果嬗变术
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.transmutation.desc = 解锁将紫颂果用作可以将一些方块转换为其它方块的方块嬗变催化剂的能力
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.perfect_recover = 完美复原
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.perfect_recover.desc = 像荧石一样会掉落其合成材料的方块将必定掉落足够的合成材料以重新合成
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.more_wheat = 超多小麦
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.more_wheat.desc = 在收获完全成熟的小麦作物时有很小的概率收获两个小麦
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.green_thumb = 绿拇指
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.green_thumb.desc = 拥有此能力的玩家周围的作物将会生长的更快
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.hungry_farmer = 饥饿农夫
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.hungry_farmer.desc = 让吃东西成为被动行为。（自动喂食）
reskillable.unlock.reskillable.roadwalk = 陆上行走
